00:00:07.720 --> 00:00:09.780
Drupe and Noom have
expanded globally

00:00:09.780 --> 00:00:12.470
by localizing their
apps on Google Play.

00:00:12.470 --> 00:00:16.200
drupe increased their
daily active users by 300%,

00:00:16.200 --> 00:00:18.450
and actions per
average daily user

00:00:18.450 --> 00:00:21.245
